---
---
<section id="testimonios" class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-white overflow-hidden w-full relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-24" data-aos="fade-up">
            <span class="text-gold font-bold tracking-[0.6em] uppercase text-[9px] mb-6 block border-b border-gold/10 pb-4 inline-block mx-auto">Nuestros Clientes</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-black font-black italic tracking-tighter leading-tight mt-6">
                Relatos de <br> <span class="metal-gold-text pr-8">Distinción</span>
            </h4>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-12 lg:p-14 border border-black/5 shadow-[0_30px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] rounded-sm transition-all duration-700 ease-out hover:-translate-y-4 hover:shadow-[0_45px_100px_-20px_rgba(184,134,11,0.25)] hover:border-gold/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center group" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="relative mb-10">
                    <div class="w-[80px] h-[80px] rounded-full overflow-hidden border-[1px] border-gold/50 p-1 group-hover:border-gold transition-colors duration-700">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=200&h=200&fit=crop" 
                             alt="Elena V." 
                             class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 scale-105 group-hover:scale-100">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h6 class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-black text-black mb-1">Elena V.</h6>
                <p class="text-gold text-[8px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold mb-8">Cliente</p>
                
                <div class="max-w-[280px]">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-[14px] font-serif italic leading-[1.8] pr-2 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-700">
                        "Encontrar piezas que no se ven en ninguna parte ha sido un cambio total en mi estilo personal. La selección es impecable."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 w-8 h-px bg-gold/30 group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-1000"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-12 lg:p-14 border border-black/5 shadow-[0_30px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] rounded-sm transition-all duration-700 ease-out hover:-translate-y-4 hover:shadow-[0_45px_100px_-20px_rgba(184,134,11,0.25)] hover:border-gold/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="relative mb-10">
                    <div class="w-[80px] h-[80px] rounded-full overflow-hidden border-[1px] border-gold/50 p-1 group-hover:border-gold transition-colors duration-700">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=200&h=200&fit=crop" 
                             alt="Ricardo M." 
                             class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 scale-105 group-hover:scale-100">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h6 class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-black text-black mb-1">Ricardo M.</h6>
                <p class="text-gold text-[8px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold mb-8">Cliente</p>
                
                <div class="max-w-[280px]">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-[14px] font-serif italic leading-[1.8] pr-2 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-700">
                        "La atención personalizada me ayudó a elegir las prendas perfectas para mi viaje. Se nota el alto criterio en cada detalle."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 w-8 h-px bg-gold/30 group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-1000"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white p-12 lg:p-14 border border-black/5 shadow-[0_30px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] rounded-sm transition-all duration-700 ease-out hover:-translate-y-4 hover:shadow-[0_45px_100px_-20px_rgba(184,134,11,0.25)] hover:border-gold/30 flex flex-col items-center text-center group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="relative mb-10">
                    <div class="w-[80px] h-[80px] rounded-full overflow-hidden border-[1px] border-gold/50 p-1 group-hover:border-gold transition-colors duration-700">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?q=80&w=200&h=200&fit=crop" 
                             alt="Sofía G." 
                             class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full filter grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 scale-105 group-hover:scale-100">
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <h6 class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-black text-black mb-1">Sofía G.</h6>
                <p class="text-gold text-[8px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold mb-8">Cliente</p>
                
                <div class="max-w-[280px]">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-[14px] font-serif italic leading-[1.8] pr-2 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-700">
                        "No es solo adquirir prendas, es sentir que cada pieza es única. La exclusividad de sus colecciones limitadas es real."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-10 w-8 h-px bg-gold/30 group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-1000"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
